title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 19 2022

description:
Clay and Buck continue to broadcast from KNRS in Salt Lake City where, at dinner last night, Buck had the best gluten-free cupcakes of his life. Crime in Democrat cities continues to rise. Why Dr. Oz is a million times better than John Fetterman. Who's going to watch the new super woke tv show, She-Hulk?
